距離位置（忽然而來的皮球）； 手部的位置沒有必要的擺動，這是一種犯規； 以手中持有的物件（例如︰衣服、護脛等）接觸皮球同樣被視為犯規； 用擲出的物體（如球鞋、護脛等）擊中皮球被視為犯規。 所以，根據球員當時和皮球距離的位置，如果太近根本未能躲避，而雙手沒有不必要的非自然動作，裁判就會判此等情況為波打手了。<br />\n<br />\n屌你禁區中手就實判12m咩  睇多次啦米路隻手向後收緊阿"},{"pid":"766708b009ddb85a585fc5d620baebb6e82ee12d","tid":615933,"uid":105275,"like":0,"dislike":5,"score":-5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-03T19:38:12.000Z","msg":"對唔住各位皇迷 睇返慢鏡我錯 係黑左個手球 都係黑呀<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"189cc959c579e602833af2ca2408a32a2abf247b","tid":615933,"uid":37218,"like":6,"dislike":11,"score":-5,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2018-04-03T19:39:38.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/04/04/033907_7b2fa59ff3f215d6b4649aa2d95aca99.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F04%2F04%2F033907_7b2fa59ff3f215d6b4649aa2d95aca99.jpg&h=d973812a&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n球證唔判關皇馬撚事<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e6ce17e67c5a84957c6673d61805dadd38a1f592","tid":615933,"uid":23809,"like":10,"dislike":2,"score":8,"quote":{"pid":"189cc959c579e602833af2ca2408a32a2abf247b","tid":615933,"uid":37218,"like":6,"dislike":11,"score":-5,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2018-04-03T19:39:38.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/04/04/033907_7b2fa59ff3f215d6b4649aa2d95aca99.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F04%2F04%2F033907_7b2fa59ff3f215d6b4649aa2d95aca99.jpg&h=d973812a&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n球證唔判關皇馬撚事<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-03T19:40:36.000Z","msg":"第一日睇波?  ball hand 同hand ball識分咩阿<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7e3c54decf124febbd